                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              A technique for the effective and automatic reuse of classical compiler optimizations
                     on multithreaded code
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Pramod G. Joisha, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Robert S. Schreiber, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Prithviraj Banerjee, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Hans J. Boehm, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Dhruva R. Chakrabarti
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              POPL '11: Proceedings of the 38th annual ACM SIGPLAN-SIGACT symposium on Principles of programming
                     languagesJanuary 2011, pp 623–636https://doi.org/10.1145/1926385.1926457
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              A large body of data-flow analyses exists for analyzing and optimizing sequential
                  code. Unfortunately, much of it cannot be directly applied on parallel code, for reasons
                  of correctness. This paper presents a technique to automatically, aggressively, ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Android operating system has become one of the most popular smartphone platforms.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Cross-layer based erasure code to reduce the 802.11 performance anomaly: when FEC meets ARF

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Wireless networks have been widely accepted and deployed in our world nowadays. Consumers
                  are now accustomed to wireless connectivity in their daily life due to the pervasiveness
                  of the 802.11b/g and wireless LAN standards. Specially, the emergence of ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Predicting the performance of application-specific NoCs implemented on FPGAs

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          A Comparison of Performance and Accuracy of Measurement Algorithms in Software
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Omid Alipourfard, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            •

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          SOSR '18: Proceedings of the Symposium on SDN ResearchMarch 2018, Article No.: 18, pp 1–14https://doi.org/10.1145/3185467.3185475
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Many network functions are moving from hardware to software to get better programmability
                  and lower cost. Measurement is critical to most network functions because getting
                  detailed information about traffic is often the first step to make control ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                A Multivariate Characterization and Detection of Software Performance Antipatterns
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Alberto Avritzer, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Ricardo Britto, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  •

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Barbara Russo,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ICPE '21: Proceedings of the ACM/SPEC International Conference on Performance EngineeringApril 2021, pp 61–72https://doi.org/10.1145/3427921.3450246
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Context. Software Performance Antipatterns (SPAs) research has focused on algorithms
                  for the characterization, detection, and solution of antipatterns. However, existing
                  algorithms are based on the analysis of runtime behavior to detect trends on ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Performance and cost optimization for multiple large-scale grid workflow applications

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Using software-based performance counters to expose low-level open MPI performance
                     information
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • David Eberius, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • Thananon Patinyasakdikul, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • George Bosilca
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            EuroMPI '17: Proceedings of the 24th European MPI Users' Group MeetingSeptember 2017, Article No.: 7, pp 1–8https://doi.org/10.1145/3127024.3127039
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            This paper details the implementation and usage of software-based performance counters
                  to understand the performance of a particular implementation of the MPI standard,
                  Open MPI. Such counters can expose intrinsic features of the software stack that are
                  ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              High-performance code generation for stencil computations on GPU architectures
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Justin Holewinski, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Louis-Noël Pouchet, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • P. Sadayappan
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              ICS '12: Proceedings of the 26th ACM international conference on SupercomputingJune 2012, pp 311–320https://doi.org/10.1145/2304576.2304619
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Stencil computations arise in many scientific computing domains, and often represent
                  time-critical portions of applications. There is significant interest in offloading
                  these computations to high-performance devices such as GPU accelerators, but these
                  ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Generating energy-efficient code for parallel applications specified by streaming
                     task graphs with dynamic elements
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Sebastian Litzinger, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Jörg Keller
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                PMAM '20: Proceedings of the Eleventh International Workshop on Programming Models and Applications
                     for Multicores and ManycoresFebruary 2020, Article No.: 8, pp 1–10https://doi.org/10.1145/3380536.3380544
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Streaming task graphs are a high-level construct used to specify parallel applications
                  operating on streams of data, and energy-efficient code meeting data throughput requirements
                  can be generated automatically. Tasks can be parallel themselves, so that ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Refactoring Object-Relational Database Applications by Applying Transformation Rules
                     to Develop better Performance

                  languages such as C, C++, and Java along with the embedded statements expressed in

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            PPOpenCL: a performance-portable OpenCL compiler with host and kernel thread code
                     fusion
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • Ying Liu, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              •

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            OpenCL offers code portability but no performance portability. Given an OpenCL program
                  X specifically written for one platform P, existing OpenCL compilers, which usually
                  optimize its host and kernel codes individually, often yield poor performance for
                  ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Reducing human effort and improving quality in peer code reviews using automatic static
                     analysis and reviewer recommendation
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Vipin Balachandran
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              ICSE '13: Proceedings of the 2013 International Conference on Software EngineeringMay 2013, pp 931–940
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               Peer code review is a cost-effective software defect detection technique. Tool assisted
                  code review is a form of peer code review, which can improve both quality and quantity
                  of reviews. However, there is a significant amount of human effort involved ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Automated analysis of multithreaded programs for performance modeling
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Alexander Tarvo, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Steven P. Reiss
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ASE '14: Proceedings of the 29th ACM/IEEE international conference on Automated software engineeringSeptember 2014, pp 7–18https://doi.org/10.1145/2642937.2642979
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                The behavior of multithreaded programs is often difficult to understand and predict.
                  Synchronization operations and limited computational resources combine to produce
                  complex non-linear dependencies between a program's configuration parameters and its
                  ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Developing a high-performance quantum chemistry program with a dynamic scripting language
